column2: amce_age <- cj(dfcj, choice_indicator ~ expected_pension + firearms + fossil_fuels + may_employ_children + racial_diversity_mgmt + gender_equal_pay, id = ~survey_id, weights = ~weights, estimate = "amce", by = ~age.cat)
